org.assertj.swing.fixture
Class JListFixture

java.lang.Object
  org.assertj.swing.fixture.AbstractComponentFixture<S,T,D>
      org.assertj.swing.fixture.AbstractJComponentFixture<S,T,D>
          org.assertj.swing.fixture.AbstractJPopupMenuInvokerFixture<JListFixture,JList,JListDriver>
              org.assertj.swing.fixture.JListFixture
All Implemented Interfaces:
ItemGroupFixture<JListFixture>, JComponentFixture<JListFixture>, JPopupMenuInvokerFixture, MouseInputSimulationFixture<JListFixture>
public class JListFixture
extends AbstractJPopupMenuInvokerFixture<JListFixture,JList,JListDriver>
implements ItemGroupFixture<JListFixture>

Supports functional testing of JLists.

The conversion between the values given in tests and the values being displayed by a JList renderer is performed by a JListCellReader. This fixture uses a BasicJListCellReader by default.

Author:
Alex Ruiz, Yvonne Wang, Fabien Barbero
